title: Thin Mint S'more
description:
Camp Chef S'more of the Week | The Thin Mint

With a perfect combination of minty freshness, dark chocolate, and gooey marshmallow, this s'more recipe is sure to please even the most avid s'more traditionalist. 

Ingredients:

• Graham
• Marshmallow
• Mint Patties
